{"tid":1890563,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國 FBI 跳過正常招標和零售程序，直接採購口罩、消毒液","createTime":"2020-02-21T09:12:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-21T10:10:55.000Z","uid":287269,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"9680dde61ad312fbe3330e7b958c335b3c09017a","tid":1890563,"uid":287269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T09:12:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.cnbc.com/amp/2020/02/20/fbi-orders-40000-in-hand-sanitizer-and-face-masks-in-case-of-a-coronavirus-pandemic-in-us.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2Famp%2F2020%2F02%2F20%2Ffbi-orders-40000-in-hand-sanitizer-and-face-masks-in-case-of-a-coronavirus-pandemic-in-us.html&d=8qD7g5vOfNqkLkogRxTPVK0IH4hhGWFtD%2BQErH2Rjq0%3D&h=ac0ca9be\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cnbc.com/amp/2020/02/20/fbi-orders-40000-in-hand-sanitizer-and-face-masks-in-case-of-a-coronavirus-pandemic-in-us.html</a><br />\n<br />\n文章提到FBI放棄招標而直接選擇某一消毒液 供應商係因為其殺菌效能最好。而放棄從零售途徑購買係因為有時間嘅逼迫切性。<br />\n<br />\nThe agency justified awarding the contract to PDI without a formal competitive bidding process because &quot;they are the number one rated in healthcare because of this kill time.&quot;<br />\n<br />\nThe bureau added that it is making the purchase directly from manufacturers 3M and PDI rather than through retailers &quot;because of the urgency of this request.&quot;"},{"pid":"092ba06dbbe6419c3b90b30dd48f4bd88f962acd","tid":1890563,"uid":118910,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T09:14:19.000Z","msg":"香港正苦：出一條有十萬項嚴苛規則嘅招標<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea25120eecc98d1cf2d9e3c848edf50ad38990c8","tid":1890563,"uid":68689,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T09:14:52.000Z","msg":"香港政府：因時間嘅迫切性及避免複雜既程序，政府會使用招標程序。"},{"pid":"747b4368bf5638fc8fbd63c338d01458c18d9b11","tid":1890563,"uid":103916,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T